headline.print_headline: Finnair Buys 8 Airbus Planes in $2.3 Billion Deal
headline.main: Finnair Buys 8 Airbus Planes in $2.3 Billion Deal

lead_paragraph: Finnair PLC says it has ordered eight Airbus A350 aircraft in a deal valued at some 1.9 billion euros ($2.3 billion).
